<p>

Heindl has painted over eighty colorful album covers for Putumayo World Music. She interprets Putumayo’s music through simple lines, bold colors, and lively scenes that capture the cultures represented on each album. An avid traveler herself, Heindl has been able to witness many of these cultures first-hand and frequently draws on her own experiences for inspiration.  Her sketchbooks include drawings from trips to <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../533/14533.xml">
